data.description: Welcome to 903 Broadway Street, a hidden gem located in the desirable town of Surf City. This single family home offers 3 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms. When arriving, you will notice the spacious driveway, charming backyard, fresh exterior paint and 2 newer HVAC systems. Upon entering the home, you will be greeted by two bedrooms, each with their own full bathrooms and private decks. Upstairs you will find the third bedroom which also offers a private bathroom and deck with tranquil marsh, sound and ICW views. The top floor is complete with your living area, fully renovated kitchen and dining area, wet bar, half bathroom and utility closet. Off of the kitchen, you can enjoy ocean views from the covered deck. This home is move in ready with newer paint throughout as well as upgraded floors. Whether enjoying the spacious backyard, ground level deck or views from 1 of the 4 decks, you will be able to find the perfect spot to end your day. This property is also within walking distance to your local shops, restaurants and night life. So what are you waiting for, schedule your showing today before this hidden gem gets taken off the market.
